1. *Reke* su puno odgovorne za zdravlje lokalnog ekosistema. (Rivers are very responsible for the health of the local ecosystem.)
2. *Rekama* se često povezuje priroda Srbije. (Rivers are often associated with the nature of Serbia.)
3. *Reka* Dunav se proteže kroz veći deo Evrope. (The River Danube runs through much of Europe.)
4. *Rečke* su se preplavile u toku prošlogodišnje poplave. (The streams were flooded during last year's flood.)
5. *Rekama* se bave istraživači iz celog sveta. (Researchers from all over the world are engaged in rivers.)